trans-unit.source: The event argument passed to the <see cref="E:System.Web.Security.PassportAuthenticationModule.Authenticate" /> event by a <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.PassportAuthenticationModule" />.
Since there is already an identity at this point, this is useful mainly for attaching a custom <see cref="T:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal" /> object to the context using the supplied identity.
